                </p>
                <p>
                    In this game, you play a ship that is <strong
                        class="text-white"
                        >attracted to the ground regardless of its orientation</strong
                    > in a futuristic setting. Our goal is to create a dynamic game
                    with a gameplay loop based on completing a level 100% and competing
